<h1 align="center">🛋️ EmptyCup Interior Designers Listing</h1>

<p align="center">
  A stylish mobile-friendly web app to discover and shortlist interior designers.<br>
  Built with a lightweight <strong>Flask API backend</strong> and a <strong>vanilla JS frontend</strong>, styled pixel-perfect as per the Figma design.
</p>

<p align="center">
  <img src="frontend/assets/logo.png" alt="EmptyCup Logo" height="50">
</p>

---

## ✨ Features

- 📱 **Mobile-first responsive layout**
- 🗂️ View interior designer cards with ratings, experience, pricing, and contact info
- ❤️ **Shortlist** your favorite designers
- 🔁 Toggle view: All designers / Shortlisted only
- ⚡ Fast and lightweight – no frameworks used on frontend
- 🎯 Clean, modular folder structure and codebase

---

## 📁 Folder Structure

emptycup-Full  Stack assignment/
├── backend/
│ ├── app.py # Flask API for serving designers
│ └── designers.json # Static JSON with mock data
└── frontend/
├── index.html # Main UI
├── styles.css # Responsive styling
├── script.js # Shortlist logic + data fetching
└── assets/ # Figma icons and logos
